Text: NWP System Notice New Fuel Factors effective Post Date November Category NEWS BRIEFS Subcategory MISCELLANEOUS Subject New Fuel Factors effective Notice Text All Shipper Letter Date Time hrs TO All Shippers SUBJECT New Fuel Factors Effective December On November FERC issued a draft order accepting Northwest Pipelines new fuel factors to be effective December The new fuel factors will be Rate Schedules TF TF TI Please contact your Marketing Services Representative for more information WGPW rwcc
